1
00:00:00,380 --> 00:00:03,380
I'll be waiting for you to confess, then!

2
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:09,590
Alright!
It's time to announce the winner of our "Prince" contest!

3
00:00:09,590 --> 00:00:10,680
(Cheers)

4
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:13,560
Will all our Prince candidates
please come to the stage!

5
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:18,810
(Cheers)

6
00:00:18,810 --> 00:00:23,610
(That's right, this all started...
when Mizukuchi-san dumped me...)

7
00:00:23,610 --> 00:00:26,320
How pathetic.

8
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,280
Who!?

9
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:29,610
The school festival is in one month.

10
00:00:29,610 --> 00:00:33,160
You're going to become the Prince
and show her what she's missing.

11
00:00:33,660 --> 00:00:35,080
You're being so dramatic.

12
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:37,290
Your eyes really are a beautiful color.

13
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:39,750
There. Perfect.

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,250
(When did I start...)

15
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,710
(...feeling this way?)

16
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:49,670
Shh...!

17
00:00:54,390 --> 00:00:57,520
This year's Tensho Festival Prince is...

18
00:00:57,520 --> 00:01:00,600
(Drumroll)

19
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:03,020
(So that's it... I've fallen this hard for Yuki...)

20
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:05,730
I'm going to make you a prince.

21
00:01:05,730 --> 00:01:06,980
(Drumroll)

22
00:01:06,980 --> 00:01:10,150
From the Department of Psychology, a third-year!
Motomiya Makoto!

23
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:11,450
(Cheers and applause)

24
00:01:11,450 --> 00:01:14,240
Alright, Motomiya-kun!
As our new Prince,

25
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:16,740
who is the one person you want to share your feelings with right now?

26
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:19,750
That person is...

27
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,960
Yuki!!

28
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,380
I can't believe he actually screamed it out loud.
